Please calm down.

277
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:14,319
Police officers fighting is against the rules.

278
00:23:23,519 --> 00:23:27,400
I'm the kind of person
who believes in reciprocation.

279
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:29,200
You've helped me so much,

280
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:31,079
So, I'll help you once.

281
00:23:31,079 --> 00:23:34,920
Don't you love catching the triads?

282
00:23:34,920 --> 00:23:36,400
Then I'll help you catch

283
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:39,839
the most powerful triad leader, Xia Liu Yi.

284
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,839
How about that?

285
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:53,200
My treat.

286
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:11,359
Inspector Xie.

287
00:24:12,119 --> 00:24:15,480
In fact, you're just a useless cop.

288
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:18,200
You can't save anyone.

289
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:21,839
You only make those
who believe in you die faster.

290
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:36,919
Congratulations.

291
00:24:36,919 --> 00:24:39,399
You've officially become
an officer of the ICAC.

292
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:43,240
Jia Hua, don't worry.

293
00:24:43,240 --> 00:24:44,359
I will definitely be a good officer

294
00:24:44,359 --> 00:24:47,480
who upholds justice like you.

295
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:49,119
All the best.

296
00:25:22,359 --> 00:25:24,119
Boss!

297
00:25:24,119 --> 00:25:26,040
Call for you.

298
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:27,759
Damn.

299
00:25:27,759 --> 00:25:29,680
Great gun, boss.

300
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,799
Heavy bleeding.

301
00:25:31,799 --> 00:25:34,480
This gun is hard to handle.

302
00:25:34,480 --> 00:25:36,879
For He Chu San.

303
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:41,000
I'll take him to the shooting range today.

304
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:42,919
Let him be bolder.

305
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:45,960
Is the place ready?

306
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:47,319
It's clean.

307
00:25:47,319 --> 00:25:49,879
Not a single fly can get in.

308
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:02,280
- Dong Dong.
- What is it?

309
00:26:03,279 --> 00:26:07,799
Have you ever tried
letting someone worry about you?

310
00:26:07,799 --> 00:26:09,240
Who?

311
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:10,960
Worried about me?

312
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:15,079
There are plenty who want to cut me down.

313
00:26:18,240 --> 00:26:21,200
That idiot He Chu San.

314
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:23,960
He says he's worried about me.

315
00:26:23,960 --> 00:26:26,279
I, Xia Liu Yi, Dual Blades Xia.

316
00:26:26,279 --> 00:26:28,680
Do I need a university student
to worry about me?

317
00:26:30,465 --> 00:26:31,680
A student?

318
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:34,079
A student should just be holding a lollipop.

319
00:26:34,079 --> 00:26:35,599
Why?

320
00:26:38,559 --> 00:26:40,359
Why have a gun?

321
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:45,559
Forget it.

322
00:26:48,079 --> 00:26:49,960
It would be good
to teach him some self-defense.

323
00:26:49,960 --> 00:26:52,480
So, he won't worry in the future.

324
00:27:07,559 --> 00:27:10,400
I heard he was parachuted in.
[Gangcheng Bank]

325
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:12,119
What kind of guy is he?

326
00:27:12,119 --> 00:27:14,720
He's related to both you and me.

327
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:17,000
The Hang Seng Index has gone up again.

328
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:22,319
Let's work.

329
00:27:22,319 --> 00:27:23,960
Let's get to work.

330
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:31,039
Do you need me to go over the details again?

331
00:27:31,039 --> 00:27:32,399
No worries.

332
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:35,680
I'll just find someone.

333
00:27:36,559 --> 00:27:38,200
I want him.

334
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:43,799
Please have him contact me directly
so that we can get started.

335
00:27:43,799 --> 00:27:45,119
Sam.

336
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,680
Hello, I'm Jason.

337
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,480
Nice to see you.

338
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:56,280
Hello, Jason. Nice to meet you, too.

339
00:27:57,079 --> 00:27:59,079
I just got back to Hong Kong.

340
00:27:59,079 --> 00:28:01,680
And I'm not familiar with many things.

341
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,000
I may need a local guy

342
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:05,799
to help me with some personal stuff.

343
00:28:05,799 --> 00:28:07,000
I think...

344
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,160
Sam.

345
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:11,240
Sam will be a great choice.

346
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,720
Okay, Sam.

347
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:15,279
You'll be in charge of Jason during this time.

348
00:28:15,279 --> 00:28:16,400
- Okay.
- Great.

349
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:18,559
The Hang Seng Index
has broken the 1,000 point mark.

350
00:28:18,559 --> 00:28:20,119
Passion.

351
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:46,720
Are you kidding me?

352
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:49,280
Did he get that big phone as a decoration?

353
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:57,799
The whole building's power is out.

354
00:28:57,799 --> 00:28:59,960
Still not off work.

355
00:29:07,240 --> 00:29:08,680
Jason.

356
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:10,879
This is our project plan.

357
00:29:12,559 --> 00:29:14,559
- Let's leave together.
- Okay.

358
00:29:15,319 --> 00:29:17,000
Sam.

359
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,519
You're so talented.

360
00:29:18,519 --> 00:29:20,839
It's a bit beneath you to be here.

361
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:29,759
They just said you're the hardest working one.

362
00:29:29,759 --> 00:29:31,040
Why?

363
00:29:38,519 --> 00:29:40,319
I...

364
00:29:49,480 --> 00:29:51,720
A gun, for you.

365
00:30:09,480 --> 00:30:11,000
Sorry.

366
00:30:15,319 --> 00:30:16,759
Same time tonight, I'll pick you up.

367
00:30:16,759 --> 00:30:18,559
Tonight?

368
00:30:18,559 --> 00:30:20,680
I have an important guest to entertain tonight.

369
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:21,880
I might not be able to make it.

370
00:30:21,880 --> 00:30:23,400
A guest to entertain?

371
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,960
I'll hang up now.

372
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:30,000
How dare you hang up on me!

373
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,400
What kind of job is so important?

374
00:30:31,400 --> 00:30:34,159
I'll make you resign sooner or later.

375
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:38,280
I haven't eaten yet.

376
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:41,319
Your girlfriend?

377
00:30:41,319 --> 00:30:43,599
She sounds like she has quite a temper.

378
00:30:43,599 --> 00:30:45,079
No, no, no.

379
00:30:45,759 --> 00:30:47,480
Just a friend.

380
00:30:50,039 --> 00:30:51,720
They're a good person.

381
00:30:56,400 --> 00:30:58,319
Seems like it's not just a regular friendship.

382
00:30:58,319 --> 00:31:00,200
You've known each other a long time?

383
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:04,559
Let's continue.

384
00:31:54,279 --> 00:31:56,480
He drew a little dog.

385
00:31:57,799 --> 00:31:59,640
11.3%.

386
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:03,839
The expected growth
for this year is 26.51 million.

387
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:26,519
I thought you were working overtime here.

388
00:32:26,519 --> 00:32:29,200
Turns out you're flirting with someone here.

389
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:31,279
You misunderstood.

390
00:32:31,279 --> 00:32:33,160
We're working.

391
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:34,680
Sam.

392
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:37,040
Is he... your friend?

393
00:32:39,561 --> 00:32:40,960
Hi.

394
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,559
I'm Jason.

395
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:46,280
Nice to meet you.

396
00:32:49,279 --> 00:32:50,520
Don't speak English here.

397
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:51,559
Shut it. Shut up.

398
00:32:51,559 --> 00:32:52,799
Did you hear me?

399
00:32:52,799 --> 00:32:54,119
What are you doing? We really are working.

400
00:32:54,119 --> 00:32:55,919
He Chu San.

401
00:33:00,319 --> 00:33:01,480
You...

402
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:03,599
You're always like this.

403
00:33:03,599 --> 00:33:05,640
You really misunderstood.

404
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:07,480
Sorry, Jason.

405
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,919
You misunderstood.

406
00:33:18,599 --> 00:33:21,000
Let's see how I'll deal with you.

407
00:33:26,079 --> 00:33:29,200
I guess I do feel a little reluctant.

408
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,480
He Chu San.

409
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:46,559
Are you using the phone as decoration?

410
00:33:46,559 --> 00:33:47,839
Why didn't you answer my call?

411
00:33:47,839 --> 00:33:49,639
Have you eaten?

412
00:33:58,559 --> 00:34:00,119
Just right.

413
00:34:01,599 --> 00:34:04,399
Recently, there have been
some investment reports.

414
00:34:07,039 --> 00:34:08,400
Are you kidding me?

415
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:09,440
- Liu Yi.
- Shut up.

416
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:11,519
Why did you bring me here?

417
00:34:11,519 --> 00:34:12,920
I told you it was a misunderstanding.

418
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,880
He Chu San, stop talking to me.

419
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,439
Come with me.

420
00:34:17,180 --> 00:34:19,660
Don't you have some gender
and emotional awareness disorder?

421
00:34:19,660 --> 00:34:21,140
I think you're just messing with me.

422
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:22,800
You like men, don't you?

423
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:23,960
You bastard, you're fooling me.

424
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:26,079
- Messing with me, huh?
- I'm not messing with you.

425
00:34:26,079 --> 00:34:27,079
You aren't?
If I must say,

426
00:34:28,079 --> 00:34:29,320
I'll find a woman to sleep with you,

427
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:31,180
and after you sleep with her,
you'll be cured of all your issues.

428
00:34:31,180 --> 00:34:33,119
I don't need to prove anything to you.

429
00:34:33,119 --> 00:34:35,220
I would never do something like that.

430
00:34:35,220 --> 00:34:37,560
I would never come to this kind of mess...

431
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:42,500
This place.

432
00:34:44,599 --> 00:34:46,920
This kind of place?

433
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:49,220
Is this kind of place beneath you now?

434
00:34:49,220 --> 00:34:52,880
Does this place tarnish your reputation
as a university graduate?

435
00:34:52,880 --> 00:34:54,800
I'm the owner of this place.

436
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:57,519
I hang out here every day.

437
00:34:57,519 --> 00:34:59,480
Since you look down on this place,

438
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:01,760
why do you follow me here every day?

439
00:35:10,679 --> 00:35:12,760
You're not that kind of person.

440
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,400
Where's Mei?

441
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:20,200
Get Mei here.

442
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:44,760
Liu Yi.

443
00:35:48,480 --> 00:35:50,039
Liu Yi.

444
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,679
It takes a thousand days to raise an army.

445
00:36:02,679 --> 00:36:04,640
But a moment to use them.

446
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,959
One thousand, solved.

447
00:36:12,199 --> 00:36:13,960
Did you see that?

448
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:15,599
A pure, pristine girl.

449
00:36:15,599 --> 00:36:17,960
Liu Yi, take it easy.

450
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:19,960
I've only slept with her once.

451
00:36:19,960 --> 00:36:22,280
Just the right match for you, the chaste guy.

452
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:25,639
Let her teach you what it means to be a man.

453
00:36:25,639 --> 00:36:26,959
Liu Yi!

454
00:36:35,039 --> 00:36:36,040
I'm leaving.

455
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:37,319
Stop.

456
00:36:38,079 --> 00:36:39,119
Is this a place where you can

457
00:36:39,119 --> 00:36:40,400
just come and go as you please?

458
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,560
Do you think this is a public restroom?

459
00:36:43,880 --> 00:36:45,879
Didn't you bring me here?

460
00:36:48,599 --> 00:36:51,000
But I didn't tell you to leave.

461
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,400
He Chu San, I'm telling you,

462
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:53,840
if you don't sleep with her today,

463
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,719
I'll strip her immediately,

464
00:36:55,719 --> 00:36:57,720
and throw her to the dogs on the streets.

465
00:37:00,239 --> 00:37:02,760
Sir, save me.

466
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:04,400
Save me.

467
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:06,839
Save me, mister.

468
00:37:09,760 --> 00:37:11,720
You wouldn't do that.

469
00:37:12,639 --> 00:37:14,719
Someone!

470
00:37:14,719 --> 00:37:16,920
- Where are they?
- Liu Yi, what do you need?

471
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:17,920
Take off her clothes.

472
00:37:17,920 --> 00:37:19,320
No problem.

473
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,519
Come on, come on.

474
00:37:20,519 --> 00:37:21,520
She's so fierce.

475
00:37:21,520 --> 00:37:22,639
Are you crazy?

476
00:37:22,639 --> 00:37:23,639
- Come here.
- Save me!

477
00:37:23,639 --> 00:37:25,960
- Come here!
- Save me!

478
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:28,039
Come here!

479
00:37:28,039 --> 00:37:29,480
Always misbehaving.

480
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:31,399
I'll beat you to death.

481
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:34,360
Mister, save me.

482
00:37:34,360 --> 00:37:35,800
You won't listen to Liu Yi, huh?

483
00:37:35,800 --> 00:37:36,960
I'll beat you to death.

484
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,960
Sir, save me.

485
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,800
Be quiet!

486
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:41,960
I'll beat you to death.

487
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:43,719
Mister, save me.

488
00:37:43,719 --> 00:37:46,159
- Will you listen?
- Save me! Save me!

489
00:37:46,159 --> 00:37:48,640
You're the one I'm beating.

490
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:52,920
- Save me!
- Will you listen?

491
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:53,960
Stop hitting me.

492
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:55,559
Don't hit me anymore.

493
00:37:55,559 --> 00:37:57,399
Save me!

494
00:37:58,400 --> 00:37:59,800
Okay.

495
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:02,080
I'll do as you say.

496
00:38:08,639 --> 00:38:10,880
Sir, you're here.

497
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,880
Come over here.

498
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:13,400
Make sure to keep Miao company, okay?

499
00:38:13,400 --> 00:38:14,960
Be smart. Have fun.

500
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:16,280
Smile.

501
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,480
Ma'am, I'm leaving.

502
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:18,559
Where is she going?

503
00:38:18,559 --> 00:38:22,280
Chu San.

504
00:38:26,719 --> 00:38:28,479
I understand.

505
00:38:30,599 --> 00:38:33,039
They're even holding hands.

506
00:38:33,039 --> 00:38:35,039
This guy is really in love.

507
00:38:35,039 --> 00:38:36,480
He dares to steal the big boss's woman.

508
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:38,079
No way.

509
00:38:38,079 --> 00:38:39,400
What are you doing?

510
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,719
Get back to work.

511
00:38:40,719 --> 00:38:42,119
What are you looking at?

512
00:38:42,119 --> 00:38:44,119
Mommy, I want that, too.

513
00:38:44,119 --> 00:38:44,960
You want your head cut off?

514
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:47,000
Do you want the money or not? Go back to work.

515
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,039
Back to work.

516
00:38:48,039 --> 00:38:49,719
What are you doing? Go inside.

517
00:38:49,719 --> 00:38:51,800
Be smart.

518
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,399
Hold hands.

519
00:38:54,639 --> 00:38:56,159
A date.

520
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:57,880
Hold hands.

521
00:38:57,880 --> 00:39:03,800
Date, hold hands.

522
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:07,120
Are you boxing or torturing yourself?

523
00:39:11,880 --> 00:39:13,800
I heard you spent 20,000

524
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:15,960
buying a woman for the student.

525
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,680
Are you crazy?

526
00:39:18,599 --> 00:39:20,999
What does my money have to do with you?

527
00:39:22,320 --> 00:39:24,119
He likes you.

528
00:39:24,119 --> 00:39:25,360
You sleep with him.

529
00:39:25,360 --> 00:39:27,479
Then you can save 20,000.

530
00:39:28,119 --> 00:39:29,159
Cui Dong Dong.

531
00:39:29,159 --> 00:39:30,880
What are you talking about?

532
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,840
I'm just talking nonsense.

533
00:39:32,840 --> 00:39:34,920
He risked his life to save you back then.

534
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:36,880
He almost died delivering a message for you.

535
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:38,960
A top university student skipped class

536
00:39:38,960 --> 00:39:41,760
and came to join the underworld.

537
00:39:41,760 --> 00:39:43,199
If he doesn't like you,

538
00:39:43,199 --> 00:39:45,319
could he be an undercover?

539
00:39:46,679 --> 00:39:47,719
I treat him as...

540
00:39:47,719 --> 00:39:49,519
I treat him as a friend.

541
00:39:49,519 --> 00:39:50,920
I treat him as a brother.

542
00:39:50,920 --> 00:39:53,280
So, a brother goes on dates with a girl.

543
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:56,280
Why are you jealous and punching the sandbag?

544
00:39:57,559 --> 00:39:59,720
I'm not jealous.

545
00:40:06,159 --> 00:40:07,559
Xia Liu Yi.

546
00:40:07,559 --> 00:40:10,239
I don't care whether
you two sleep together or not.

547
00:40:10,239 --> 00:40:11,719
But that He Chu San...

548
00:40:11,719 --> 00:40:13,159
Every day, he's looking all handsome,

549
00:40:13,159 --> 00:40:14,519
taking that girl away from me,

550
00:40:14,519 --> 00:40:16,760
and then sweetly bringing her back.

551
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:18,679
Girls are getting all wild at heart

552
00:40:18,679 --> 00:40:20,679
and don't even want to do business anymore.

553
00:40:20,679 --> 00:40:21,679
I don't care about all that.

554
00:40:21,679 --> 00:40:23,519
Just get him away from me.

555
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:28,519
Whatever loss you have, I'll cover it for you.

556
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:35,559
Xia Liu Yi.

557
00:40:35,559 --> 00:40:38,839
You're just asking for trouble.

558
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:45,600
Chu San.

559
00:41:15,599 --> 00:41:18,399
- Dong Dong.
- So early.

560
00:41:23,639 --> 00:41:26,079
College student.

561
00:41:26,079 --> 00:41:27,760
Waiting for Mei?

562
00:41:31,519 --> 00:41:33,320
So sweet.

563
00:41:33,320 --> 00:41:36,680
When are you planning to take her away from me?

564
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:43,000
Mei belongs to Xia Liu Yi.

565
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,999
He'll be upset.

566
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:48,159
You're really adaptable.

567
00:41:48,159 --> 00:41:50,319
A real talent.

568
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:56,839
No, wait.

569
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:59,960
Xia Liu Yi, this eternal virgin,

570
00:41:59,960 --> 00:42:03,640
actually told you that Mei has been with him?

571
00:42:04,679 --> 00:42:07,039
That's hilarious.

572
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:12,360
That's what he said.

573
00:42:12,360 --> 00:42:15,639
His personality is really awkward.

574
00:42:15,639 --> 00:42:17,360
He talks tough,

575
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:20,119
but when it comes to someone he likes,

576
00:42:20,119 --> 00:42:22,360
he doesn't dare to even glance at them twice.

577
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:24,480
So, after all these years,

578
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,879
no one has paid him any attention.

579
00:42:30,039 --> 00:42:32,480
Xia Liu Yi is in the hospital.

580
00:42:32,480 --> 00:42:34,239
What?

581
00:42:34,239 --> 00:42:35,920
Not sure what triggered it.

582
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:38,680
A single sneeze landed him in the hospital.

583
00:42:39,400 --> 00:42:40,519
Are you going to see him?

584
00:42:40,519 --> 00:42:42,200
Which hospital is he at?

585
00:42:49,760 --> 00:42:51,280
College student.

586
00:42:52,119 --> 00:42:56,039
Are you serious about Xia Liu Yi?

587
00:43:03,159 --> 00:43:04,280
Yes.

588
00:43:19,480 --> 00:43:22,959
Xia Liu Yi is like a stone,
smelly and hard in a cesspit.

589
00:43:23,880 --> 00:43:26,800
Your passion alone won't do anything.

590
00:43:26,800 --> 00:43:29,519
You have to let him figure it out himself.

591
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:36,600
Maybe Mei is your trump card.

592
00:44:30,800 --> 00:44:32,439
Dong Dong.

593
00:44:33,360 --> 00:44:35,600
Why are you helping me?

594
00:44:43,039 --> 00:44:44,999
I'm not helping you.

595
00:44:45,920 --> 00:44:47,839
I'm helping Xia Liu Yi.

596
00:44:52,559 --> 00:44:55,680
Ever since Xiao Man and Qing Long died,

597
00:44:56,519 --> 00:44:59,879
he's lived every day in regret.

598
00:45:00,880 --> 00:45:05,320
It wasn't until he met you
that he started acting like a human again.

599
00:45:05,320 --> 00:45:11,319
So, I hope you can help him
move on to a new life.

600
00:45:13,159 --> 00:45:15,519
What's going on?

601
00:45:15,519 --> 00:45:17,360
He hit me!

602
00:45:17,360 --> 00:45:18,960
Get out here!

603
00:45:18,960 --> 00:45:21,800
Don't you know this is my turf?

604
00:45:27,320 --> 00:45:31,080
Boss, your food is here.

605
00:45:47,280 --> 00:45:49,399
I... He...

606
00:45:51,519 --> 00:45:53,439
Go explain it yourself.

607
00:45:58,719 --> 00:46:00,679
I heard you're sick.

608
00:46:00,679 --> 00:46:02,680
I came to check on you.

609
00:46:07,599 --> 00:46:09,280
Which one do you want?

610
00:46:11,519 --> 00:46:13,120
This one.

611
00:46:37,079 --> 00:46:38,879
Put your leg down.

612
00:46:52,599 --> 00:46:54,840
Here's plain congee and century egg
with lean pork congee.

613
00:46:54,840 --> 00:46:56,640
What would you like to have?

614
00:47:06,639 --> 00:47:07,760
And these.

615
00:47:07,760 --> 00:47:10,360
This is salted radish made by Dad.

616
00:47:10,360 --> 00:47:12,280
It doesn't look very appealing,

617
00:47:12,280 --> 00:47:13,319
but it smells amazing.

618
00:47:13,319 --> 00:47:14,560
Try it.

619
00:47:15,599 --> 00:47:16,879
No.

620
00:47:25,079 --> 00:47:27,000
Find a place to sit.

621
00:47:27,000 --> 00:47:28,399
Your foot.

622
00:47:52,960 --> 00:47:54,720
Liu Yi.

623
00:47:55,880 --> 00:47:58,719
I'm sorry about that night.

624
00:47:58,719 --> 00:48:01,400
I shouldn't have made you angry.

625
00:48:01,400 --> 00:48:03,959
I know you meant well.

626
00:48:20,960 --> 00:48:23,160
Mei is really nice.

627
00:48:26,239 --> 00:48:28,239
I'm happy when I'm with her.

628
00:48:28,239 --> 00:48:29,839
Thank you.

629
00:48:47,960 --> 00:48:49,360
Liu Yi.

630
00:48:49,360 --> 00:48:51,200
I want to show you something.

631
00:48:52,760 --> 00:48:54,239
What is it?

632
00:48:54,239 --> 00:48:55,920
Look.

633
00:48:55,920 --> 00:48:58,519
A rose.

634
00:48:58,519 --> 00:49:00,800
I got it tattooed just for Mei.

635
00:49:01,559 --> 00:49:03,160
Do you like it?

636
00:49:04,519 --> 00:49:06,880
Have you lost your mind!

637
00:49:06,880 --> 00:49:08,920
It's just a relationship! Why get a tattoo?

638
00:49:08,920 --> 00:49:11,800
Don't you know a tattoo lasts a lifetime?

639
00:49:13,960 --> 00:49:15,680
It's about to fade.

640
00:49:37,480 --> 00:49:38,920
What are you doing?

641
00:49:38,920 --> 00:49:40,919
You really care about me.

642
00:49:43,320 --> 00:49:45,280
Care about what?

643
00:49:46,000 --> 00:49:47,760
I'm just afraid...

644
00:49:47,760 --> 00:49:50,039
I'm afraid Uncle He would hit you
if he knew about your tattoo.

645
00:49:50,039 --> 00:49:52,080
Dad wouldn't do that.

646
00:49:58,000 --> 00:49:59,720
Besides...

647
00:50:00,480 --> 00:50:01,480
To me...

648
00:50:01,480 --> 00:50:04,200
Loving someone is a lifetime commitment.

649
00:50:16,800 --> 00:50:18,600
Don't you agree?

650
00:50:25,760 --> 00:50:27,439
How would I know?

651
00:50:40,119 --> 00:50:41,480
Liu Yi.

652
00:50:41,480 --> 00:50:44,640
Do you want to watch
a new movie together next week?

653
00:50:46,599 --> 00:50:48,039
No.

654
00:50:48,039 --> 00:50:50,199
Go with your girlfriend.

655
00:50:50,199 --> 00:50:51,880
Fine.

656
00:50:51,880 --> 00:50:54,679
Then I'll watch it with her first.

657
00:50:54,679 --> 00:50:56,480
If it's good, I'll tell you.

658
00:50:56,480 --> 00:50:58,400
Forget it.

659
00:50:58,400 --> 00:51:00,039
I've been busy lately.

660
00:51:03,559 --> 00:51:06,480
You won't be busy during the New Year, right?

661
00:51:06,480 --> 00:51:08,000
Dad asked whether

662
00:51:08,000 --> 00:51:09,999
we should celebrate the New Year together.

663
00:51:10,800 --> 00:51:11,840
He Chu San.

664
00:51:11,840 --> 00:51:13,719
My whole squad from Xiaoqi Hall...

665
00:51:13,719 --> 00:51:15,320
They're all lined up
waiting to celebrate with me.

666
00:51:15,320 --> 00:51:17,280
Why would I celebrate New Year at your place?

667
00:51:17,280 --> 00:51:18,839
I'm not going.

668
00:51:21,519 --> 00:51:23,599
Here it comes, the dishes are served.

669
00:51:23,599 --> 00:51:26,720
Wishing you wealth in the new year.

670
00:51:27,480 --> 00:51:28,679
Liu Yi, I didn't expect you

671
00:51:28,679 --> 00:51:30,519
to take the time to celebrate New Year with us.

672
00:51:30,519 --> 00:51:32,800
I also want to celebrate with you guys.

673
00:51:32,800 --> 00:51:35,920
Son, I'm not blaming you,
but Liu Yi is our guest.

674
00:51:35,920 --> 00:51:37,920
You shouldn't make him do it himself, really.

675
00:51:37,920 --> 00:51:40,239
Uncle He, it's nothing major.

676
00:51:40,239 --> 00:51:41,480
You don't know.

677
00:51:41,480 --> 00:51:43,960
Lately, he's been neglecting family matters.

678
00:51:43,960 --> 00:51:46,399
Whenever he's free, he goes chasing girls.

679
00:51:47,800 --> 00:51:49,800
I almost forgot.

680
00:51:51,280 --> 00:51:52,320
I mean, really...

681
00:51:52,320 --> 00:51:53,800
It's fine that you're chasing girls.

682
00:51:53,800 --> 00:51:56,840
- But you don't even bring them home.
- Exactly.

683
00:51:56,840 --> 00:52:00,400
My wine is meant for my future daughter-in-law.

684
00:52:00,400 --> 00:52:02,640
That's right.

685
00:52:03,320 --> 00:52:05,000
Liu Yi.

686
00:52:05,000 --> 00:52:06,320
Home-brewed glutinous rice wine.

687
00:52:06,320 --> 00:52:08,239
- Have a glass.
- No, no, thanks.

688
00:52:08,239 --> 00:52:09,239
Just try it.

689
00:52:09,239 --> 00:52:11,679
Glutinous rice wine
won't make you drunk quickly.

690
00:52:11,679 --> 00:52:13,079
Don't be shy.

691
00:52:13,079 --> 00:52:14,679
Chu San, why are you tugging me?

692
00:52:14,679 --> 00:52:15,840
I haven't even finished talking.

693
00:52:15,840 --> 00:52:17,679
Am I such a narrow-minded father?

694
00:52:17,679 --> 00:52:19,679
If I'm getting a daughter-in-law,
shouldn't you bring her home?

695
00:52:19,679 --> 00:52:21,639
Let me see her first.

696
00:52:21,639 --> 00:52:23,760
That's all I'm saying.

697
00:52:25,480 --> 00:52:29,760
- Come on, come on.
- Dad, our fortunes aren't even matched yet.

698
00:52:29,760 --> 00:52:31,159
Let him drink a little less.

699
00:52:31,159 --> 00:52:32,480
Drinking glutinous rice wine...

700
00:52:32,480 --> 00:52:35,360
That's how you celebrate the New Year.

701
00:52:35,360 --> 00:52:38,280
Without glutinous rice wine,
it doesn't count as the New Year.

702
00:52:38,280 --> 00:52:40,480
Drinking it warms your heart
for the coming year.

703
00:52:40,480 --> 00:52:41,559
Exactly, exactly.

704
00:52:41,559 --> 00:52:43,000
And you said our fortunes aren't even matched.

705
00:52:43,000 --> 00:52:46,239
Fei said they all went to her shop.

706
00:52:46,239 --> 00:52:47,840
Yes, hear me out.

707
00:52:47,840 --> 00:52:48,960
That day, he brought a girl over

708
00:52:48,960 --> 00:52:50,400
to eat beef offal at the shop.

709
00:52:50,400 --> 00:52:52,559
She's a very pretty girl with long hair.

710
00:52:52,559 --> 00:52:53,679
She looks so beautiful.

711
00:52:53,679 --> 00:52:56,000
- Fei.
- They look perfect together.

712
00:52:56,000 --> 00:52:58,559
Fei, eat something.

713
00:52:58,559 --> 00:53:00,120
Eat first.

714
00:53:01,880 --> 00:53:04,199
All right, let's eat.

715
00:53:04,199 --> 00:53:05,760
But when chasing girls,

716
00:53:05,760 --> 00:53:08,080
he's all calculative and deliberate.

717
00:53:08,719 --> 00:53:09,759
Dad, don't speak. Eat.

718
00:53:09,759 --> 00:53:11,320
I really want to have a grandson.

719
00:53:11,320 --> 00:53:13,000
Me, too.

720
00:53:13,000 --> 00:53:15,960
Next New Year, you must bring her home.

721
00:53:15,960 --> 00:53:18,280
Yes, the more the merrier at home.

722
00:53:18,280 --> 00:53:24,080
I'd be so happy to have a chubby grandson.

723
00:53:25,000 --> 00:53:26,800
Come on, come on.

724
00:53:33,119 --> 00:53:34,519
You guys eat first.

725
00:53:34,519 --> 00:53:36,760
I'm going to the bathroom.

726
00:53:36,760 --> 00:53:39,280
All right, go ahead.

727
00:54:18,480 --> 00:54:20,480
Liu Yi.

728
00:54:20,480 --> 00:54:22,399
You're upset?

729
00:54:25,880 --> 00:54:27,840
No, not at all.

730
00:54:27,840 --> 00:54:29,280
I'm leaving.

731
00:54:35,000 --> 00:54:36,839
Where are you going?
